reviewText:
Water temple stage;

Game-breaking glitch stopped progress.

Square Enix killed me.

I would rate it as 6/10.

Pros:

- Nice Graphics;
- Smart Puzzles;
- Smart Control;

Cons:

- Glitches;
- Unsync of multiplayer due to high ping. It makes the game bug and you have to start all over again;

The game is focused on multiplayer, therefore it should work, right? Well, it doesn't happen here. If you want to play with your friends of find people playing, make sure they have a really low ping, otherwise the game will simply stop working all the time.
It has a nice potential however, it lacks quality and I bet it has not been tested by the ones who decided to sell it.
